query:
SELECT 
  productId, 
  brand, 
  name, 
  CASE 
    WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND description != '' THEN 'YES' 
    ELSE 'NO' 
  END as has_desc,
  CASE 
    WHEN specifications IS NOT NULL AND JSON_LENGTH(specifications) > 0 THEN JSON_LENGTH(specifications)
    ELSE 0 
  END as spec_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM product_categories WHERE productId = p.productId) as category_count
FROM products p
WHERE brand IN ('Agilent', 'Thermo Fisher Scientific', 'Shiseido')
LIMIT 10;
